---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Maine Cannabis Market Analysis | Maine Dispensary Guide" description="Analysis of Maine's cannabis market size, growth trends, opportunities, and competitive landscape for dispensary owners.">
  <article>
    <header>
      <h1>Maine Cannabis Market Analysis</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Understanding the opportunity in Maine's cannabis industry</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Market Overview</h2>
      <p>Maine's cannabis market has grown significantly since retail sales launched in 2020. The combination of medical and adult-use programs creates a substantial opportunity for dispensary operators.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Market Size & Growth</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Metric</th><th>Estimate</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Total Market Size (2025)</td><td>$200-250M</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Projected Growth (Annual)</td><td>10-15%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Medical Patients</td><td>50,000+</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Adult-Use Customers</td><td>Growing rapidly</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Market Drivers</h2>
      
      <h3>Population & Demographics</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>1.3+ million Maine residents</li>
        <li>Growing retirement population</li>
        <li>Medical cannabis program expansion</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Tourism</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Summer tourism season</li>
        <li>Fall foliage visitors</li>
        <li>Winter ski destinations</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Competition</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Limited licenses available</li>
        <li>Barriers to entry create opportunity</li>
        <li>First-mover advantage in underserved areas</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Product Categories</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Category</th><th>Market Share</th><th>Growth</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Flower</td><td>45-50%</td><td>Stable</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Concentrates</td><td>20-25%</td><td>Growing</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Edibles</td><td>15-20%</td><td>Growing</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Tinctures</td><td>5-10%</td><td>Stable</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Topicals</td><td>3-5%</td><td>Growing</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Competitive Landscape</h2>
      <p>Maine's cannabis market is less saturated than larger states, creating opportunity for new operators. Key competitors include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Well-established multi-state operators</li>
        <li>Local independent dispensaries</li>
        <li>Medical dispensary operators expanding to adult-use</li>
        <li>Vertical integrators</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Opportunities</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Underserved markets outside Portland</li>
        <li>Premium positioning</li>
        <li>Delivery services</li>
        <li>Edibles and infused products</li>
        <li>Medical patient loyalty programs</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Challenges</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Regulatory complexity</li>
        <li>Tax burden</li>
        <li>Banking restrictions</li>
        <li>Competition from existing operators</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>$200-250M market with 10-15% annual growth</li>
        <li>Opportunity in underserved areas</li>
        <li>Multiple product categories growing</li>
        <li>Barriers to entry protect established operators</li>
        <li>First-mover advantage in new markets</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>Market estimates are approximate and based on available industry data.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2, section h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  section h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  section h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
</style>
